OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FFootball players could be sanctioned
OL,7,Fin the future for covering their
OL,8,Fmouths when talking to opponents.
OL,10,FGianluca Prestianni is under
OL,11,Finvestigation for alleged racial abuse
OL,12,Ftowards Real Madrid's Vinicius Junior
OL,13,Fin a Champions League match last week.
OL,15,FWhat he said to Vinicius is disputed,
OL,16,Fwith Prestianni vehemently denying
OL,17,Fusing racist language. The
OL,18,FArgentinian's mouth was covered when
OL,19,Fhe appeared to say something to
OL,20,FVinicius.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
