CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FFIFA is understood, as reported by the
OL,7,FPress Association, to be keen to
OL,8,Fexplore ways to tackle the issue. It
OL,9,Fis thought to have raised the idea of
OL,10,Fintroducing a deterrent to such
OL,11,Fbehaviour at a technical meeting on
OL,12,FFriday, ahead of the International
OL,13,FFootball Association Board (IFAB)
OL,14,Fannual general meeting in Wales on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
