PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FOne insider referred to it as
OL,7,F"Vinicius' Law", and the British
OL,8,Fassociations ` who make up the IFAB
OL,9,Falongside FIFA ` were understood to be
OL,10,Freceptive to the idea, although, as it
OL,11,Fis so early in discussions, the
OL,12,Fpracticalities of enforcing it would
OL,13,Fneed careful consideration.
OL,15,FThis is understood to be just the
OL,16,Fstart of the discussion, however, and
OL,17,Fit is not expected that any formal
OL,18,Fproposal to tackle the issue will be
OL,19,Fbrought forward immediately.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
