CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FFIFA is also believed to have raised
OL,7,Fthe penalty for players walking off
OL,8,Fthe pitch from a yellow to a red card
OL,9,Fin the wake of the chaos at the end of
OL,10,Fthe Africa Cup of Nations final
OL,11,Fbetween Senegal and Morocco.
OL,13,FFIFA has been approached for comment
OL,14,Fby the Press Association.
OL,16,FVinicius was allegedly abused during
OL,17,FReal Madrid's win over Benfica in
OL,18,FLisbon on February 17.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
