CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FThe 25-year-old left the field after
OL,7,Freporting a member of the Benfica team
OL,8,F` whom the Spanish side later claimed
OL,9,Fto have been Prestianni ` to referee
OL,10,FFrancois Letexier.
OL,12,FThe match was paused in line with UEFA
OL,13,Fregulations, resulting in a stoppage
OL,14,Fin play lasting 10 minutes, with
OL,15,FVinicius going on to play the full
OL,16,Fgame in Real's 1-0 win.
OL,18,FIt came after the Brazilian forward
OL,19,Fhad given his team the lead with a
OL,20,Fwonderful individual strike five
OL,21,Fminutes into the second half.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FAfter celebrating in front of the home
OL,7,Ffans, the 25-year-old became visibly
OL,8,Fupset about something said to him and
OL,9,Fimmediately informed Letexier.
OL,11,FAfter the game, Vinicius posted in
OL,12,FPortuguese on his Instagram story:
OL,13,F"Racists are, above all, cowards. They
OL,14,Fneed to put their shirts in their
OL,15,Fmouths to demonstrate how weak they
OL,16,Fare."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
