PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FHe started for Real in Wednesday's
OL,7,Freturn and had the final word as the
OL,8,FSpanish giants reached the last 16,
OL,9,Fwith a cool 80th-minute finish
OL,10,Fsecuring a 2-1 win on the night and 3-
OL,11,F1 aggregate success.
OL,13,FUEFA had imposed a provisional
OL,14,Fsanction on Prestianni on Monday,
OL,15,Fruling him out of the tie, although
OL,16,Fthe winger had travelled to Madrid as
OL,17,Fpart of the Benfica squad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
