PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772265857
OL,3,CFIFA exploring 'Vinicius Law' idea to
OL,4,Cpunish players who cover their mouth
OL,6,FThe Portuguese club had appealed
OL,7,Fagainst the decision to ban
OL,8,FPrestianni, but UEFA dismissed the
OL,9,Fcase on Wednesday afternoon.
